<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201218/54f3596c1bdc46a3826ff755d0900120.jpeg" /></p>
<p>山西省新增境外输入确诊病例1例</p>
<p><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201218/318fb4c8e66349949215a894eed51169.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
